Using the Calculator Application
Use your finger to swipe up on your phone screen.
Tap on the Calculator application to open it.
You can use the app just as you would use a physical calculator.


Figuring Out the Bill
Add the cost of the coffee and sandwich together to get the total amount owed. 
  
  The coffee cost $1.00, so tap on '1' '.' '0' '0' and then the '+' sign. 
  The sandwich cost $2.00, so tap on '2' '.' '0' '0' and then the '+' sign.

The total bill should be $3.00.
